Class LeaderboardController.LeaderboardRow

java.lang.Object
main.java.com.team.game.controller.LeaderboardController.LeaderboardRow
Enclosing class:
LeaderboardController
public static class LeaderboardController.LeaderboardRow extends Object
Represents a single row in the leaderboard table. Stores a player’s rank, username, and high score.
